cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CR 

The paper focuses on person attribute recognition using deep convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of deeper networks and interpretation of classification decisions also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of datasets and analysis of results suggests a focus on multimedia (cs.MM) and potentially also on computer security (cs.CR) in the context of video surveillance.
